% Stress: 1000 matching tag-binds
0 /ok tag
1000 { /ok { 1 add /ok tag } tag-bind } repeat
tag-value 1000 eq
    (tag-bind: stress 1000 match) rt-ok clear

% Stress: 1000 non-matching tag-binds (pass-through)
